306.source:
function hitPipes() {
    var self = this
    for(var i=0; i<this.pipes.length; i++){
        if(this.pipes[i].getName()=='tubeDown'
            && this.bird.getPosition().x >= this.pipes[i].getPosition().x
            && this.bird.getPosition().x <= this.pipes[i].getPosition().x+this.pipes[i].getExtent().x
            && self.bird.getPosition().y <= this.pipes[i].getExtent().y)
                return true
        else if(this.bird.getPosition().x >= this.pipes[i].getPosition().x
            && this.bird.getPosition().x <= this.pipes[i].getPosition().x+this.pipes[i].getExtent().x
            && self.bird.getPosition().y <= this.y
            && self.bird.getPosition().y >=this.y-this.pipes[i].getExtent().y)
                return true
        }
    return false
}
